parameters:
\tl<Gundead Executive> Hmph, so you've finally made it this far. Well, I guess
I'll personally take care of you.
\>\tr<Red Signal> You despicable Gandead executive!! Prepare yourself!

\>\tr<Red Signal> We have the authority to immediately suppress and
execute with lethal force on-site based on the Gandead Countermeasures
Act!!
\tl<Gundead Executive> Very well, I'll make sure to defeat you thoroughly.

I have executed the enemy executive with extreme punishment. I will
now return.
There is no chance of winning in the current state.
There is no chance of winning in the current state.
I obtained the mental stabilizer medication!

I am someone who supports fighting heroines. Would you like to buy our
products?

\c[3]Defeat the small fry and reach the boss. Clear the stage by
defeating the boss.

\c[3]You can communicate with Blue and Yellow from the menu. You might
be able to hear some hints.

\c[3]If two people are being held captive again, you can instead
confirm the current situation (H scene).

\c[3]When your suit is destroyed, your defense decreases but your
attack power increases. Additionally, if you win while being
completely humiliated, you can acquire double the experience points.

\c[3]If the battle feels slow, you can speed it up by pressing shift.
If you want to revert, press shift again. Also, if you want to hide
the message window, you can do so by pressing ctrl.
\tr<Red Signal> Ugh... I messed up... What about my senpais...

\tr<Red Signal> I can't even establish communication... Where on earth...
We need to regroup quickly...

\c[3] Let's go rescue Blue and Yellow. We can confirm the current
state of humiliation through communication. If we keep losing, it will
progress rapidly.

\c[3] During team separation, it is overwhelmingly disadvantageous,
but when fighting alone or with two people, it becomes a situation of
adversity, and all values will continue to recover for a certain
period of time.
\tr<Red Signal> Are you okay? I will rescue you.
I rescued the citizens. I obtained PP.
\tr<Small Girl> Ahhhh!! I'm too late to escape!! Someone help meeeeee!
I obtained a large recovery potion!
I obtained a large recovery potion!

Welcome, welcome! We have a wide selection of items perfect for
fighting women.
